data.description: Wonderful home in Gretna's desirable Remington Ridge neighborhood! 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 3 car ranch with main floor office. Spacious open living area. This home features 2x6 exterior construction, solid core interior doors, and plenty of windows for added light. The kitchen has a double oven and walk-in pantry with plenty of room to entertain. Primary bedroom boasts walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom with two vanities. Large corner lot with 6' vinyl fence and a large patio. No neighbors across the street and a view of rolling hills. The basement has a huge rec room, bedroom, bath, and exercise space, as well as lots of storage. You won't want to miss this beautiful home. Close to schools and shopping. AMA. No showings after 7:00 pm.
